Recapping about the meanBooks app: The meanBooks application is done using express on top of NodeJs using mongoose and mongodb.

*The app has books collection with authors sub-document: One book can be written by multiple authors. 
    So, authors is an array.
*CRUD operations on the application's main document (books) is perfomed.
*CRUD operations on the application's main sub-document(authors array) is performed as well.
*The meanBooks application has API hardening.
*Proper url paths, routes and separation of concern is perfomed.